# DEV — Features to build

<!-- devx-empty-state-start -->
> **What goes here:** one bullet per spec file under `dev/`. `/devx` no-args
> picks the top `[ ]` ready item. Checkbox conventions: `[ ]` ready, `[/]`
> in-progress, `[-]` blocked, `[x]` done, `~~…~~` deleted. The Status field
> in each spec's frontmatter is the source of truth — the checkbox here
> mirrors it. This empty-state header auto-deletes once this file holds
> three or more items.
<!-- devx-empty-state-end -->

